# Code Quality Guidelines

## Architecture
- Follow MVVM architecture patterns consistently
- Keep views focused on UI logic only
- Maintain clear separation of concerns
- Use services for reusable business logic

## SwiftUI Best Practices
- Prefer SwiftUI views over UIKit when possible
- Keep view components small and focused
- Use @State and @Binding appropriately
- Follow SwiftUI lifecycle management guidelines

## Data Management
- Use appropriate data persistence methods (Core Data/CloudKit)
- Implement proper error handling for data operations
- Follow CRUD operation best practices
- Maintain data privacy and security 